Reasons for incorporating in Nevada

1.  Favorable corporate laws.
2.  No state corporate income tax.
3.  No state personal income tax.
4.  No franchise tax.
5.  Stockholders are not of public record.
6.  Minimal reporting and disclosure requirements.
7.  Virtual office/presence plans available for Nevada address and phone/fax services.
```
